<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٨ - مُكَمِّلًا <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مُّوضِحَةَ ابْنِ نَاجِي»</span> ... مُضِيئَةً فِي ظُلَمِ الدَّيَاجِي<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٩ - وَهْوَ بِسَبْقٍ حَائِزٌ ثَنَائِي ... مُسْتَوْجِبُ التَّفْضِيلِ وَالدُّعَاءِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٠ - فَاللهُ يَقْضِي بِعَظِيمِ الْمَغْنَمِ ... لِي وَلَهُ - غَدًا - وَّكُلِّ مُسْلِمِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>***<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١١ - وَقَدْ رَوَى حُذَيْفَةُ الصَّحَابِي ... سُؤَالَهُ فِي جِلَّةِ الْأَصْحَابِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>